latestPosts.caption:
Sometimes the universe has a plan you can’t see 🌟

We went to the same middle school, knew all the same people, but never met until we were 19. Started as best friends and 15 years later we’re married with beautiful children 💕

They say serendipity is finding something wonderful when you’re not looking for it. That’s exactly what happened to us. We were in each other’s orbit for YEARS but weren’t ready for each other until the perfect moment ✨

Sometimes the best love stories start with friendship. Sometimes timing is everything. Sometimes what’s meant for you will find you when you’re ready.

Double tap if you believe everything happens for a reason ✨
